data.description: Come see this beautiful home in an amazing location, with a highly motivated seller! The serene, and sought after neighborhood of Meander Point is exactly where you will love calling home! With Six bedrooms and Four bathrooms, this home more than covers your needs for space. The home features two living rooms on the main level and a bonus room upstairs with views of the canyon. The large kitchen is inviting, ready to make large meals, or host a quiet dinner party out on the patio. The backyard opens up to the parklike settings of the community. The homes original listing price has been reduced by $100K to reflect motivation and a market modification. Bring Offers!
